5:
Wahahaha! It feels like it's been a
long time since I walked into the
Academy like this!
8:
Well, it actually HAS been quite a
while. So much so that we ended up
getting a request to pull you back
into class...
17:
Y-yeah, I know! Let's get the
make-up classes and papers done
so we can get this crisis behind me!
23:
Oh! Hey, everyone! It's been a while.
Made any good golems lately?
25:
Y-yes, somehow or other, we
managed... B-but when did you get
back? Wait, where did you even go
in the first place?!
28:
Ah, um... Well, I had a lot of technical
research to carry out, along with...
practical experience in something I
like to call "prison studies"...
32:
A-anyway! Here's a souvenir for the
Golem Club!
35:
Th-this... What?! Is such a theory
even possible? A-and look at this
one! The approach is incredible—
39:
Wahaha! These are a compilation of
the discoveries made during my
time away. What do you think? I'm
sure these will inspire your creativity!
42:
Use this information as a
springboard for the creation of
novel golems whose design defies
conventional thinking!
45:
W-we'll do our best! But... I don't
know how many years it will take for
us to really grasp these concepts!
46:
Creating golems that completely
defy common sense in the way you
do is far beyond what we're capable
of...
52:
But still, I can't believe you were
doing such incredible research that
whole time... Dedalia, you're really—
54:
W-well, we've gotta head to class,
so please excuse us! We'll share
your findings with the others!
74:
An entire week! Everyone's been
avoiding me for a week! Why? Am I
being bullied?!
77:
Such is the life of a lonely genius,
perhaps! But that STILL wouldn't
explain the sudden ostracizing!
81:
I prepared my findings for them in
the hopes that they'd be able to
keep making progress with it...
Maybe they were just being nice.
88:
That said... Well, I think they're just in
shock after being shown something
so amazing.
105:
Listen! I'm just pouting, okay?! I don't
need you to rationalize the situation
for me!
109:
Just spoil me endlessly with free
affection, okay?!
113: You're too honest with your feelings!
119: What?! I mean, who the hell are you?
123:
Um... We're a year below you,
studying chanting... But, uh! W-we
like you! We've liked you for a long
time!
131:
Huh? Wait, really?
Hang on! You can't just hit me with
that outta nowhere!
134:
I-I know. It must be weird hearing
that from strangers so suddenly...
136:
B-but still, we wanted to make sure
you knew before you left this place!
142:
Dedalia, there you are! Please take a
look at what we've been able to
achieve!
149:
Th-this... You've incorporated
multiple elements?! And this one...
Etherblood?! Wait, this drill...
152:
W-wow, this is incredible! It's far
from finished, but I can tell your
creations are packed with ambition!
155:
...Heh... Come on... You guys are
awesome!
157:
I've... always wanted to see you all
attempt something like this...
160:
I-I'm sorry... But I'm glad we were
able to pay you back in the end
after everything you've done for us.
163:
*sniffle* There you go again, talking
like I'm gonna be disappearing soon
or something...
166:
Huh? But, aren't you dropping out of
the Academy? That's why
everyone's been so busy trying to
finish their work...
173:
B-but you've been absent for ages!
Rumors of you leaving spread
around, and then—
178: What the hell are you talking about?!
181:
Seriously? You've all been swept
away by baseless rumors?!
193:
These guys are just totally in love
with me!
201: Ah! I figured out one other thing!
204:
Apparently, a few people are after
my heart, too! Ah, I'm so busy,
though! What's a girl to do? Hah!
209:
Don't you think you're getting a little
carried away?
213: I-I've got a bad feeling about this...
222:
Wahaha! They're malfunctioning!
Looks like they're a little TOO packed
with ambition!
226:
This isn't anything to laugh about!
We've gotta act fast!
230:
Yeah, yeah. Just leave it to me! I'll go
stop them!
234:
I am the golem genius, after all!
Wahahahaha!
